phrases: Why did you ignore my text yesterday?!
I mean, every day, you are like, What'cha doing?
Chiaki and I have been dating for nearly a year.
We still have not even kissed yet.
You still have not kissed, Kana?
W-Well, it is only been a year.
Is not that a bit late?
Man, that was a huge dump.
it feels more like we are siblings than dating.
Hey, Chiaki, we get along well, right?
Yeah, we are definitely in sync, at least.
Hey, are you satisfied with this?
It is not that I am not, but cannot we be closer?
I was just a toy to you, was not I?
I am not trying to be funny, here.
What about, like, kissing and stuff?
It is embarrassing for me, too, but we are in a rel
Do you really want to waste your time with me?
Do not you have a crush or something?
Wait a second, since when are we dating?!
I confessed to you last spring, remember?
Sorry, I thought that was a comedy bit.
I knew something was not right.
You would not even try to hold hands.
But you were always, like, my best friend,
I was okay with that, though,
since you were always right there.
Well, I guess we have always been close
I have been texting you nonstop
and smacking you like we are that close.
Then let us hook up properly.
I have thought about being your boyfriend, too.
But I could not tell how you felt, so I kept quiet.
I will text you like crazy.
So let us keep doing comedy bits, okay?
I am going home to sleep.
Katori-senpai, I am not feeling well today.
You had a sad look on your face.
I was sure you were heartbroken.
Sorry, should I not have asked?
But you worked up the courage, right?
That is awesome, do not you think?
You have an absolutely dazzling look on your face right now.
I am trying to cheer you up.
I do not need you to cheer me up.
You are crying in here, though.
But, it is really yourself you want to hit, is it not?
Besides, you feel better after hitting me, do not you?
Senpai was doing that on purpose?
Not that I feel grateful at all.
Let me know if you need anything.
Why do you even care so much?
Good, now you can make it to club.
Senpai's annoying, but he is a nice guy at heart.
It gets lonely without our local idol.
You have not fallen for me, have you?
Sorry I am such a hottie.
Would you like to go for lunch sometime?
I want to thank you for helping me the other day.
Okay, I will see you on Sunday.
Why is such a cute girl asking out an uggo like me?
Did I get here too early?
I have secretly been in love with this girl on my bus.
I never had the courage to talk to her.
I thought I totally creeped her out.
I never thought she would want to thank me.
Is not there no way she would invite me?
That is it, it was all in my mind!
Um, please stop staring at me.
N-No, I am not staring at all!
I do not think you are cute or anything!
I do think you are cute, but your outfit!
That is it, your outfit's cute!
I mean, not just your outfit, but...
What am I supposed to do, here?
I should not go too pricey, but...
Maybe somewhere cheap, quick, and tasty?
There is a standing soba stall right there.
You do not have to hold back.
I-It is fine, I will go home right after we are done.
No, it is not that I want to go home!
I would love to be with you forever!
D-Do not worry, I will go home right away!
I would actually noticed you on the bus every morning.
You give your seat up for seniors all the time.
I-I have to do good when I can,
because, y'know, I am a weirdo.
But when you helped me out...
Sorry to remind you about that awfulness!
She invited me out, and I am ruining it.
M-M-Maybe for the Heian Period, but this is the 21st century.
Or maybe I just look like a dorky mascot.
No, no way this could happen to me!
Do not get your hopes up
I have been getting ignored by girls for years.
No way no way no way
Do not get your hopes up!
I am not prepared for this
If it is okay with you...
You will regret getting your hopes up!
Why does she look so serious?
Do not get your hopes up!
But what if she is serious?!
The person on cleanup duty went home.
Sometimes, we chat a little these days.
It is too much for one person.
Y-Yeah, I will be right there!
I do not want to keep you from club practice, Sugawara-kun.
Why is he so eager to help?
Maybe he is a clean freak?
Do you help with cleaning often?
No, not really, but, like, since you are...
Is it something he does not want to say?
Am I doing a crappy job of cleaning?
Sorry, I will shut up and get to work.
Did she figure out how I feel?
J-Just so you know, I did not mean that in a weird way!
Sorry if I made you uncomfortable.
No, sorry I did not notice, either.
You are helping me because you noticed me, right?
I was actually interested in you.
Sorry, I never learned about this stuff.
Like, what do you want to do, Takano?
I want to get better at it.
Like, so that I can clean up better.
I think you are pretty enough as you are.
Well, I wanted to tell you...
No, maybe I am rushing things.
Wait, am I going too slow?
Sorry, I was taking too long.
I am just glad you know how I feel now.
I will ask you how you feel next time
I will learn to clean quicker.
It is not a topic that is easy to bring up.
You sure are a good person.
Wait, what are we talking about?
